ENG//RUS
/////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

Developers do not care about anything related to the game and those who play it. You have already bought it and..you see the greeting – “Support Overkill!”. You bought the PayDay for $5, that’s cool but this is not a complete game. You need to buy the DLC for $3.50 and then you'll have access to all the content that you have purchased.

So..
+ nice graphics, addictive gameplay, leveling skills (3 main branches + 1 of the DLC) gives access to new equipment and weapon sight;
+The missions will not bother;
+ Exciting achievements;
+ Voice chat, which is rarely used;
+ Single-player, Multi-player with the possibility of switching on and off bots;

- Developers have left the crude game with frequent bugs;
- Sometimes lost connection to the host in Multi-player;


Of course , the game is worth the money, but not the work of developers, which is still in an abandoned development stage.
That's why I don't advise to buy the game at full prise.
Wait for the discounts, gentlemen! :)

